snippet.title: Blocksworld - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Join the developer for a look at Blocksworld, including how you can build fun things like dinosaurs and more in this 3D building game. A Kickstarter campaign for Blocksworld is available. In Blocksworld, drag and snap building blocks together to make anything from cute characters to mighty machines.
